## General Field

A general field that can contain any field type.

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import { FieldDef } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field value = contains(FieldDef);
}
```
